full_text: Screened by NARA, 9/18/2023 Central Office 14036/392-A Hashington, D. C. Sept. 17, 1948 Place of Birth: Los Angeles, Onlif. Residence: (1932) 1135 E. 21st St., Los Angeles, Calif, Mother: GONG SESS Age 43 (1932) Natural feet Date and place of birth: KS 17-2-9 (March 18, 1891) in AI LURD Village, Sun Ning District, China. Wife: TONG SILEE : natural feet Residence: (1936) Song Lung village, Hoy San District, China. Children: (As of July 5, 1936) WONG DOON LIM : male; born OR 23-10-30 (December 6, 1934) WONG DOON CHER : male; born CR 25-1-31 (February 13, 1936) Residence of Children: China The records of this office do not contain any information concerning the subject subsequent to July 5, 1936. Identical information was furnished the District Director, Los Angeles, California, on July 8, 1948, for use in processing a petition for an immigration visa (Form I-133) filed by the subject in behalf of his elleged wife, YONG SURY GEF.
